      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Pay less or no duty on goods you store, process, repair or temporarily use
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Find out about customs special procedures that enable you to suspend, pay less or no duty on goods you import or export.
</p>

  </div>
</div>

